  "remarks": "\nMaria Vladimirovna VORONSTOVA is widely reported to be the daughter of the President of the Russian Federation Vladimir Vladimirovich PUTIN, with whom she is closely associated and from whom she has obtained a financial benefit or other material benefit. Vladimir Vladimirovich PUTIN is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019.\n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
